</taxonomicNameLabel>
, female. A, habitus, right; B, cephalosome, dorsal; C, posterior end of prosome and urosome, ventral; D, left caudal ramus, ventral; E, rostrum; F, antennule; G, antenna; H, mandible; I, maxillule; J, maxilla; K, leg 1; L, leg 2. Scale bars: A, 1 mm; B, C, 0.1 mm; D, E, K, L, 0.05 mm; F–J, 0.02 mm.
</paragraph>
